                    <span>Have you ever wondered how the duality of exhistance ought to be?  Why society seems so profoundly different from the oddness of our predetermined day?  Indulge in this great read.  There is no other - that can compete with well over six thousand years of tried and true universal truths.  You know, the unspoken beauty that eminates from our event horizon.  Not quite following me?  Get the book, read it, love it and just be.  Raise your conscience to a more universal level.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A classic document on the I Ching</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
